ue">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/u-s-charges-six-hamas-leaders-over-october-7-attack-vows-more-measures-to-come/00000191-b9c1-dffe-abf9-bdff6b460000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡讲话前几小时：摩萨德主席表示以色列愿意退出费城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/hours-before-netanyahus-speech-mossad-chief-said-israel-willing-to-exit-philadelphi/00000191-b973-d9c6-a997-bb7bef400000</link><description>撤军将在人质协议的第二阶段进行。一名以色列官员告诉《国土报》，“内塔尼亚胡的新闻发布会旨在出于政治原因破坏该协议”</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 20:36:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/hours-before-netanyahus-speech-mossad-chief-said-israel-willing-to-exit-philadelphi/00000191-b973-d9c6-a997-bb7bef400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长和政界人士参加欢乐婚礼，被谋杀的人质安息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-politicians-attend-joyous-wedding-as-murdered-hostages-laid-to-rest/00000191-b84d-d95b-a1d5-b97d2f830000</link><description>该活动的视频在社交媒体上广泛流传，联盟成员微笑、欢呼、跳舞庆祝。婚礼与赫什·戈德堡-波林和卡梅尔·盖特的葬礼在同一天举行</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 19:47:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-politicians-attend-joyous-wedding-as-murdered-hostages-laid-to-rest/00000191-b84d-d95b-a1d5-b97d2f830000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院禁止“飞马小组”传唤警察作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-bars-pegasus-panel-from-calling-cops-to-testify/00000191-b94b-dffe-abf9-bd7f6e3f0000</link><description>该小组传唤了警察网络部门的高级官员在对以色列警察使用“控制论工具”的调查中作证，尽管他们没有获得这样做的授权</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 19:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-bars-pegasus-panel-from-calling-cops-to-testify/00000191-b94b-dffe-abf9-bd7f6e3f0000</guid></item><item><title>喜欢引诱、颠覆和破坏犹太人的以色列部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-03/ty-article/.highlight/the-israeli-minister-who-loves-to-bait-subvert-and-sabotage-jews/00000191-b860-dd1b-a7db-bffe1e750000</link><description>以色列是时候用一名海外犹太人特使取代侨民事务部长阿米凯·奇克利了，他珍视生命而不是土地，播撒团结而不是分裂，他知道如何将社区团结在一起，而不是分裂他们</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 18:53:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-03/ty-article/.highlight/the-israeli-minister-who-loves-to-bait-subvert-and-sabotage-jews/00000191-b860-dd1b-a7db-bffe1e750000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡刚刚制定了以色列将如何永远统治加沙的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-just-mapped-out-how-israel-would-rule-gaza-forever/00000191-b88e-d9c6-a997-baaeb9a20000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔奈胡宣布以色列将保留对费城路线的控制，这符合他维持邪恶三位一体的愿望：总理职位、煽动反对左派和占领</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 18:51:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-just-mapped-out-how-israel-would-rule-gaza-forever/00000191-b88e-d9c6-a997-baaeb9a20000</guid></item><item><title>警惕俄罗斯，斯洛伐克从以色列购买先进防空系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/wary-of-russia-slovakia-buys-advanced-air-defense-systems-from-israel/00000191-b894-dd1b-a7db-bfde84380000</link><description>斯洛伐克正在从以色列航空航天工业公司购买六套巴拉克 MX 系统，该系统可以帮助北约成员国击落飞机、直升机和无人机，以及巡航导弹和弹道导弹</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 18:17:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/wary-of-russia-slovakia-buys-advanced-air-defense-systems-from-israel/00000191-b894-dd1b-a7db-bfde84380000</guid></item><item><title>数千人走上特拉维夫街头，呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-in-tel-aviv-calling-for-a-hostage-release-deal/00000191-b900-d13c-a39b-bf8d09ff0000</link><description>“我们无法习惯这个！这是现实，不是梦。”在哈马斯囚禁期间被杀的亚历克斯·丹西格的孙女说道。人质家属连续第四个晚上在以色列中部领导抗议活动</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 18:10:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-in-tel-aviv-calling-for-a-hostage-release-deal/00000191-b900-d13c-a39b-bf8d09ff0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第333天：消息人士告诉CNN，内塔尼亚胡“鱼雷”破坏了停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-333-netanyahu-torpedoed-truce-talks-source-tells-cnn/00000191-b88e-d13c-a39b-be8fdaa80001</link><description>消息人士告诉美国有线电视新闻网，内塔尼亚胡宣布以色列永远不会离开费城走廊，从而“破坏”了恢复人质释放谈判的努力。 10 月 7 日，战争可能导致国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡、国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令 ■ 这是战争开始 333 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-333-netanyahu-torpedoed-truce-talks-source-tells-cnn/00000191-b88e-d13c-a39b-be8fdaa80001</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长斯莫特里奇提议对2025年预算采取严格的财务措施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/israeli-finance-minister-smotrich-proposes-strict-financial-measures-for-2025-budget/00000191-b805-d13c-a39b-be8d59150000</link><description>这位极右翼部长说，我们正处于战争之中，但我们将在经济战线上共同获胜。拟议的措施包括冻结所得税等级、冻结公共部门工资、冻结最低工资以及取消游客增值税豁免。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:12:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/israeli-finance-minister-smotrich-proposes-strict-financial-measures-for-2025-budget/00000191-b805-d13c-a39b-be8d59150000</guid></item><item><title>两名西岸定居者因袭击阿拉伯以色列妇女而被起诉；一名被指控犯有恐怖罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/two-west-bank-settlers-indicted-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-one-charged-with-terror/00000191-b7a5-dffe-abf9-bfffe8200000</link><description>来自约旦河西岸定居点的两名男子被指控犯有出于种族动机的罪行，其中一名男子在袭击了来自贝都因市拉哈特的四名妇女和一名幼儿后，还被指控犯有恐怖主义罪</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:45:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/two-west-bank-settlers-indicted-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-one-charged-with-terror/00000191-b7a5-dffe-abf9-bfffe8200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡发表了一番激动人心、夸夸其谈的演讲，终结了人质协议的希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/with-a-chest-thumping-bombastic-speech-netanyahu-ends-hope-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b79b-dd1b-a7db-b7dfa8860000</link><description>在首次向人质家属请求宽恕后，以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡又回到了自己的本性：连续撒谎，无视令人不快的事实，并承诺以牺牲协议为代价留在费城路线上。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:08:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/with-a-chest-thumping-bombastic-speech-netanyahu-ends-hope-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b79b-dd1b-a7db-b7dfa8860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列烧焦的北部能否从真主党导弹袭击的废墟中崛起？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-09-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-israels-scorched-north-rise-from-the-ashes-of-hezbollahs-missiles-attacks/00000191-b74e-db99-a1d1-bf7e62610000</link><description>战争期间，加利利和戈兰高地的大片自然区域被点燃，其中包括以色列一些最受欢迎且曾经是田园诗般的景点。乘坐专为此目的制造的车辆进入一片烧焦的土地</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-09-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-israels-scorched-north-rise-from-the-ashes-of-hezbollahs-missiles-attacks/00000191-b74e-db99-a1d1-bf7e62610000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争目标、撤离人员和费城：以色列总理内塔尼亚胡的事实核查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-goals-evacuees-and-philadelphi-fact-checking-israeli-pm-netanyahu/00000191-b7b9-d95b-a1d5-bfbdfd6d0000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，内塔尼亚胡总理就一些关键问题提出了许多主张。然而，仔细观察就会发现，内塔尼亚胡并不像他表面上表现的那么诚实，他在以色列的战争目标、费城路线等问题上反复无常。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 13:52:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-goals-evacuees-and-philadelphi-fact-checking-israeli-pm-netanyahu/00000191-b7b9-d95b-a1d5-bfbdfd6d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役军人袭击为援助组织工作的加沙卡车司机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservists-assault-gazan-truck-drivers-working-for-aid-organizations/00000191-b71d-d13c-a39b-bf9d24710000</link><description>巴勒斯坦司机接受了以色列安全部门的筛查，与哈马斯或其他恐怖组织没有联系。以色列国防军士兵个人反对援助物资进入加沙地带，他们在凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点加沙一侧殴打、戴上手铐并蒙住他们的眼睛。截至本报告发布，无人受到质疑</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservists-assault-gazan-truck-drivers-working-for-aid-organizations/00000191-b71d-d13c-a39b-bf9d24710000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和犹太领导人谴责英国暂停向以色列转让部分武器的“可耻”决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-jewish-leaders-slam-u-k-s-shameful-suspension-of-some-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-b783-d9c6-a997-bfab71610000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡说：“英国的错误决定只会让哈马斯更加嚣张。”英国首席拉比谴责部分武器暂停是“乞丐的信仰”</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-jewish-leaders-slam-u-k-s-shameful-suspension-of-some-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-b783-d9c6-a997-bfab71610000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列重新占领加沙，“神圣”的费城路线将由人质尸体铺成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/the-holy-philadelphi-route-will-be-paved-with-hostages-bodies-as-israel-reoccupies-gaza/00000191-b766-d9c6-a997-bf6e0cc30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们知道，军队在加沙和埃及边境的存在过去并没有阻止哈马斯的袭击。其目标实际上是让以色列永远留在加沙，这个目标不再是愚蠢的，而是邪恶的</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 11:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/the-holy-philadelphi-route-will-be-paved-with-hostages-bodies-as-israel-reoccupies-gaza/00000191-b766-d9c6-a997-bf6e0cc30000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列西岸攻势加剧，简易爆炸物成为主要挑战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/as-israels-west-bank-offensive-intensifies-improvised-explosives-become-major-challenge/00000191-b6c0-dffe-abf9-bfff4a150000</link><description>约旦河西岸北部的大规模行动对巴勒斯坦难民营造成严重破坏，以色列军队努力“剥落”路面以发现埋设的爆炸物</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:22:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/as-israels-west-bank-offensive-intensifies-improvised-explosives-become-major-challenge/00000191-b6c0-dffe-abf9-bfff4a150000</guid></item></channel></rss>